query:
SELECT
            workspace_id,
            COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN NOT operator THEN email END)::INT as "author_count!",
            COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN operator THEN email END)::INT as "operator_count!"
        FROM usr
        WHERE email IN (
            SELECT DISTINCT username FROM audit
            WHERE timestamp > NOW() - INTERVAL '1 month'
            AND operation IN ('users.login', 'oauth.login', 'users.token.refresh')
        )
        AND workspace_id NOT LIKE 'wm-fork%'
        GROUP BY workspace_id
